latest update:

Adds:
  - In the documentation you can find links for the embeded frameworks
Changes:
  - Now developers need a special authorization to access different part of the app. (data manager, bundle editor or both)
  - In the bundle editor the components are not sorted by framework anymore, they are sorted by projects.
BugFixes:
  - No more error messages when connecting to the data manager.
Troubleshooting:
  - If you have a problem seeing your files after the update delete the admins collection in mongodb and restart the app, this will create an updated superuser with all the new authorizations.
